snippet.title: Dragonkin - The Banished | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The age of the Dragons is upon us again. Rise up with up to 4 player co-op in Dragonkin - The Banished, a action-RPG coming to Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation 5, and PC.
